dates-sensex-today-nifty-nse-bse-tata-power-neopolitan-pizza-ipo-124100100090_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-sensex-today-nifty-nse-bse-tata-power-neopolitan-pizza-ipo-124100100090_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-sensex-today-nifty-nse-bse-tata-power-neopolitan-pizza-ipo-124100100090_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Netanyahu's%20Message%2C%20Warning%20To%20Iran's%20Leaders%2C%20Assurance%20To%20Its%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20direct%20address%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Iran%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20sent%20a%20clear%20and%20forceful%20message%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Israeli%20leader's%20speech%2C%20delivered%20in%20English%20and%20subtitled%20in%20Persian%2C%20conveyed%20both%20a%20warning%20to%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20and%20an%20assurance%20to%20its%20citizens.%20The%20message%20comes%20amidst%20Israel's%20escalating%20actions%20against%20Iranian-backed%20groups%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20condemned%20Iran's%20leadership%20for%20allegedly%20prioritising%20regional%20conflicts%20over%20its%20own%20people's%20welfare.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20day%2C%20you%20see%20a%20regime%20that%20subjugates%20you%20make%20fiery%20speeches%20about%20defending%20Lebanon%2C%20defending%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Iranian%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bplunging%20the%20region%20deeper%20into%20darkness%20and%20deeper%20into%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Iran's%20support%20for%20Hezbollah%20and%20Hamas%2C%20groups%20that%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20violent%20conflicts%20with%20Israel%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%20that%20Iran's%20proxies%20were%20being%20systematically%20targeted.%20%26quot%3BIran's%20puppets%20are%20being%20eliminated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20we%20will%20not%20go%20to%20protect%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20every%20passing%20moment%2C%20the%20regime%20is%20bringing%20you%20-%20the%20noble%20Persian%20people%20-%20closer%20to%20the%20abyss%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20Iranians%20know%20their%20regime%20doesn't%20care%20a%20whit%20about%20them.%20If%20it%20did%20care%2C%20if%20it%20cared%20about%20you%2C%20it%20would%20stop%20wasting%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20futile%20wars%20across%20the%20Middle%20East.%20It%20would%20start%20improving%20your%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20all%20the%20vast%20money%20the%20regime%20wasted%20on%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20foreign%20wars%20were%20invested%20in%20your%20children's%20education%2C%20in%20improving%20your%20health%20care%2C%20in%20building%20your%20nation's%20infrastructure%2C%20water%2C%20sewage%2C%20all%20the%20other%20things%20that%20you%20need.%20Imagine%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20predicted%20a%20future%20where%20Iran%20is%20free%20from%20theocratic%20rule%2C%20envisioning%20a%20new%20era%20of%20peace%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran.%20He%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20change%20would%20come%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20sooner%20than%20people%20think.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20Netanyahu%2C%20a%20post-regime%20Iran%20would%20enjoy%20prosperity%20through%20global%20investments%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20technological%20advancements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Iran%20is%20finally%20free%20-%20and%20that%20moment%20will%20come%20a%20lot%20sooner%20than%20people%20think%20-%20everything%20will%20be%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20two%20ancient%20peoples%2C%20the%20Jewish%20people%20and%20the%20Persian%20people%2C%20will%20finally%20be%20at%20peace.%20Our%20two%20countries%2C%20Israel%20and%20Iran%2C%20will%20be%20at%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20day%20comes%2C%20the%20terror%20network%20that%20the%20regime%20built%20in%20five%20continents%20will%20be%20bankrupt%2C%20dismantled.%20Iran%20will%20thrive%20as%20never%20before%3A%20Global%20investment%3B%20massive%20tourism%3B%20brilliant%20technological%20innovation%20based%20on%20the%20tremendous%20talents%20that%20exist%20inside%20Iran.%20Doesn't%20that%20sound%20better%20than%20endless%20poverty%2C%20repression%20and%20war%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20direct%20message%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Israel's%20intensified%20operations%20against%20Iranian%20proxies.%20Days%20before%20Netanyahu's%20statement%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20executed%20a%20major%20airstrike%20that%20killed%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20at%20the%20group's%20headquarters%20in%20Beirut.%20The%20strike%20also%20reportedly%20took%20the%20life%20of%20a%20senior%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20official.%20Nasrallah's%20death%20has%20been%20met%20with%20celebration%20by%20anti-regime%20Iranians%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20deserve%20better.%20Your%20children%20deserve%20better.%20The%20entire%20world%20deserves%20better.%20I%20know%20you%20don't%20support%20the%20rapists%20and%20murderers%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%2C%20but%20your%20leaders%20do.%20You%20deserve%20more.%20The%20people%20of%20Iran%20should%20know%20-%20Israel%20stands%20with%20you.%20May%20we%20together%20know%20a%20future%20of%20prosperity%20and%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Nasrallah's%20assassination%2C%20reports%20surfaced%20that%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20secure%20location%20amid%20fears%20of%20further%20Israeli%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20reached%20new%20heights%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Iran%20launched%20over%20300%20missiles%20and%20drones%20at%20Israel%20in%20retaliation%20for%20an%20alleged%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Syria%20that%20killed%20several%20high-ranking%20IRGC%20officers.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20those%20missiles%20were%20intercepted%20by%20Israeli%20defence%20systems%2C%20with%20the%20support%20of%20a%20US-led%20coalition.%20Israel%20responded%20to%20Iran's%20actions%20with%20a%20limited%20drone%20strike%20targeting%20a%20nuclear%20research%20centre%20in%20Isfahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah's%20assassination%20also%20came%20amid%20Israel's%20campaign%20against%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20frequent%20cross-border%20attacks%20against%20Israel%2C%20allegedly%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Hamas%20during%20its%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Israel%20in%20Gaza.%20Israel%20has%20steadily%20escalated%20its%20strikes%20on%20Hezbollah%20targets%2C%20leading%20to%20significant%20losses%20within%20the%20group's%20leadership.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20month%2C%20mysterious%20explosions%20attributed%20to%20Israel%20destroyed%20Hezbollah's%20communication%20devices%2C%20injuring%20thousands%20and%20intensifying%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727749380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fp5hltaio_benjamin-netanyahu-reuters-_625x300_01_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-lebanon-in-netanyahus-message-warning-to-irans-leaders-assurance-to-its-people-6688881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20direct%20address%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Iran%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20sent%20a%20clear%20and%20forceful%20message%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-lebanon-in-netanyahus-message-warning-to-irans-leaders-assurance-to-its-people-6688881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am