20(1.5%20meters)%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchubarth%20then%20used%20semen%20from%20this%20specimen%20to%20impregnate%20various%20species%20of%20sheep%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20create%20never-before-seen%20hybrids%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20breeding%20even%20larger%20sheep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hoped%20to%20sell%20the%20resulting%20animals%20to%20%26quot%3Bcanned%26quot%3B%20hunting%20ranches%2C%20facilities%20where%20customers%20pay%20to%20shoot%20captive%20animals%2C%20and%20where%20bigger%20animals%20can%20command%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSchubarth's%20criminal%20conduct%20is%20not%20how%20Montanans%20treat%20our%20wildlife%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20US%20Attorney%20Jesse%20Laslovich.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndeed%2C%20his%20actions%20threatened%20Montana's%20native%20wildlife%20species%20for%20no%20other%20reason%20than%20he%20and%20his%20co-conspirators%20wanted%20to%20make%20more%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSchubarth's%20greed%20drove%20their%20conspiracy%20to%20bring%20to%20Montana%20parts%20of%20the%20largest%20sheep%20in%20the%20world%20from%20Kyrgyzstan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20actions%20to%20create%20hybrid%20animals%20are%20as%20unnatural%20as%20they%20are%20illegal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchubarth%2C%20whose%20ranch%20breeds%20and%20sells%20mountain%20sheep%2C%20mountain%20goats%20and%20other%20ungulates%20primarily%20for%20game%20ranches%2C%20admitted%20one%20count%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20violate%20the%20Lacey%20Act%2C%20and%20one%20of%20substantively%20violating%20the%20Lacey%20Act%20at%20an%20earlier%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lacey%20Act%20prohibits%20interstate%20trade%20in%20certain%20wildlife%20and%20is%20used%20by%20authorities%20to%20combat%20wildlife%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20prison%20sentence%2C%20Schubarth%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20a%20%2420%2C000%20fine%20to%20the%20Lacey%20Act%20Reward%20Fund%2