ated%20by%20terrorists%2C%20recorded%20lower%20figures.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0In%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20election%20held%20on%20September%2018%2C%20the%20voting%20figure%20was%20high.%20The%20turnout%20for%20the%2024%20constituencies%20across%20seven%20districts%20where%20polls%20were%20held%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20was%2061.13%20per%20cent.%20It%20was%20still%20lower%20than%20the%20record%20figure%20of%202014%2C%20which%20was%2066%20per%20cent.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20election%2C%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2056%C2%A0per%20cent%20was%20recorded%20--%20lower%20than%2057.31%20per%20cent%20of%202014.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20election%2C%20held%20after%20a%20decade%2C%20is%20the%20first%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%2C%20where%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20promised%20that%20statehood%20will%20be%20restored%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20which%20are%20contesting%20the%20polls%20as%20an%20alliance%2C%20said%20ensuring%20that%20it%20is%20done%20tops%20their%20agenda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20election%20is%20also%20a%20first%20in%20terms%20of%20inclusiveness%2C%20with%20many%20former%20separatists%20in%20fray.%20Among%20them%20are%20members%20of%20the%20banned%20Jamaat-e-Islami%2C%20the%20Islamic%20outfit%20which%2C%20along%20with%20Hurriyat%20Conference%2C%20routinely%20gave%20the%20election%20boycott%20calls%20in%20the%20Valley.%20Its%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20as%20Independents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20a%20ruling%20alliance%20with%20the%20PDP%20after%20the%20election%20results%20presented%20a%20hung%20house.%20But%20the%20alliance%20of%20the%20two%20ideologically%20mismatched%20parties%20was%20short-lived%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20came%20under%20President's%20Rule%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20time%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20witnessing%20a%20triangular%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20the%20National%20Conference-Congress%20alliance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20first%20two%20rounds%20of%20elections%20were%20held%20on%20September%2018%20and%2025%20and%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727747340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Fcr4mpkvo_jammu-and-kashmir-polls_625x300_16_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinal-phase-of-assembly-polls-in-jammu-and-kashmir-today-10-points-6687474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voting%20in%20underway%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20the%20third%20and%20last%20phase%20of%20assembly%20polls%20to%20pick%20representatives%20for%2040%20of%20its%2090%20constituencies.%20Of%20the%2040%20constituencies%2C%2024%20come%20under%20the%20Jammu%20division%20and%20the%20rest%20are%20in%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinal-phase-of-assembly-polls-in-jammu-and-kashmir-today-10-points-6687474%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'mastermind'%20behind%20India's%20biggest%20jailbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727747333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3c7d%2Flive%2F31a9f010-169a-11ef-9b16-15114b27fe47.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1dd9rj3vmyo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20389%20men%20escaped%20from%20an%20Indian%20jail%2C%20led%20by%20a%20man%20believed%20to%20have%20planned%20the%20breakout.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1dd9rj3vmyo%22