C%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20batting%20line-up%20of%20the%20side.%20He%20expressed%20his%20opinions%20on%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20lost%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20as%20the%20second%20wicket%20in%20the%20innings%2C%20everyone%20was%20waiting%20to%20see%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20bats%20at%20the%20number%20four%20position%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20To%20everyone's%20surprise%2C%20India%20sent%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20held%20back%20Kohli%2C%20only%20to%20send%20him%20later%20at%20fifth%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20talking%20about%20a%20man%20who%20got%20almost%209%2C000%20runs%20in%20Test%20cricket%20batting%20at%20No.%204%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0said%20Gavaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pant%20fell%20for%20an%2011-ball%209%2C%20Kohli%20scored%2047%20runs%20off%2035%20balls%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20fours%20and%20one%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20maestro%20Virat%20Kohli%20on%20Monday%20registered%20yet%20another%20world%20record%20to%20his%20name.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20has%20surpassed%20the%20legendary%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20reach%20the%20milestone.%20Kohli%20became%20the%20fastest%20player%20to%20score%2027%2C000%20international%20runs.%20Kohli%20achieved%20it%20in%20594th%20innings%2C%20surpassing%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20previous%20record%20(623%20innings).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20Sangakkara%20(648%20innings)%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%20(650%20innings)%20are%20the%20only%20other%20players%20to%20hit%2027000%20international%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20stumps%20on%20Day%204%20vs%20Bangladesh%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20struck%20twice%20to%20reduce%20the%20guests%20to%2026%20for%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727746680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnepmpbpg_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskar-not-happy-with-indias-ta