0owner%20of%20Atipico%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20Italian%20restaurant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20has%20also%20cooked%20for%20private%20dinners%20for%20billionaires%20and%20large%20corporate%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPertoldi%20said%20two%20simple%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20bread%20and%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20are%20always%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Matteo%20Pertoldi%2C%20a%20private%20chef%20and%20Italian%20restaurant%20owner.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20a%20chef%2C%20I%20was%20an%20engineer%20and%20architect.%20I%20came%20to%20Singapore%20in%202001%20to%20work%20in%20construction.%20However%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20job%20was%20too%20detached%20from%20people.%20If%20I%20designed%20a%20nice%20building%2C%20I'd%20see%20it%20in%20a%20magazine%2C%20but%20I%20was%20not%20in%20touch%20with%20my%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20loved%20the%20concept%20of%20hospitality%2C%20and%20cooking%20is%20a%20part%20of%20that.%20I%20always%20looked%20for%20that%20connection%20through%20food%2C%20even%20when%20studying%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20a%20small%20supper%20club%20in%20Singapore%20that%20was%20well%20received.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20cooking%20for%20people%20I%20didn't%20know%2C%20and%20they%20enjoyed%20my%20work.%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20stress%20of%20wanting%20to%20please%20people%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20still%20a%20stress%2C%20but%20unlike%20my%20job%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20positive%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20getting%20requests%20to%20cook%20for%20office%20parties%20or%20weddings%20or%20prepare%20cakes.%20My%20first%20break%20into%20the%20luxury%20sector%20was%20when%20a%20general%20manager%20of%20Panerai%2C%20an%20Italian%20luxury%20watch%20brand%2C%20asked%20for%20a%20recommendation%20from%20a%20friend%2C%20and%20they%20became%20my%20first%20client%20for%20corporate%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20of%20cooking%20on%20the%20side%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20engineering%20job%20and%20opened%20my%20restaurant%20in%202014%20%E2%80%94%20'Atipico%2C'%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bnot%20typical%26quot%3B%20in%20Italian.%20I%20think%20that%20sums%20up%20my%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20cooked%20for%20private%20events%2C%20from%20small%2C%20intimate%20dinners%20for%20two%20people%20on%20a%20superyacht%20to%20big%20corporate%20events%20with%20400%20people.%20I've%20also%20had%20the%20pleasure%20of%20cooking%20overseas%20for%20a%20millionaire%20in%20Cambodia%20and%20cooking%20for%20the%20president%20of%20Singapore%20at%20an%20embassy%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a1dae4d-202e-4916-9946-3629e44d8d1c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bread%20and%20butter%20of%20fine%20dining%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20generally%20love%20simple%20things%20when%20done%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20I'm%20cooking%20in%20a%20house%20or%20at%20a%20dinner%20party%2C%20guests%20would%20often%20go%20nuts%20for%20something%20as%20basic%20as%20bread%20and%20butter.%20There's%20something%20about%20serving%20piping%20hot%20bread%20with%20a%20quality%20slice%20of%20butter%20on%20the%20side%20%E2%80%94%20who%20doesn't%20love%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Atipico%20Bread%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fa0a72f44bdb4cfa37fa46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPertoldi's%20homemade%20bread%20is%20always%20a%20hit%20with%20his%20private%20clients.%3Cp%3EMatteo%20Pertoldi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20events%2C%20guests%20would%20often%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20your%20spread%2C%20but%20the%20bread%20and%20cakes%20really%20stood%20out.%20I%20can't%20find%20bread%20like%20this%20in%20Singapore.%20Where%20do%2