%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20there%20were%20lots%20of%20other%20founders%20and%20mentors%20to%20help%20guide%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20figure%20out%20who's%20the%20right%20chartered%20accountant%20to%20talk%20to%2C%20who's%20the%20right%20lawyer%20to%20help%20you%20draft%20agreements%2C%20all%20of%20that%20stuff%20is%20very%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Anand%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20really%2C%20really%20supportive%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhide%20said.%20There%20are%20people%20%26quot%3Btelling%20you%20about%20their%20entire%20lives%20just%20because%20they%20want%20to%20help%20you%20and%20they're%20hoping%20that%20you%20pass%20the%20favor%20onto%20the%20next%20person%20who%20moves%20to%20India%20and%20wants%20to%20start%20their%20own%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c8bff36-e855-4530-9b44-bcc7f36b0825%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20everything%20is%20perfect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20founders%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20return%20to%20India%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20no%20longer%20see%20the%20benefits%20of%20operating%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuchit%20Garg%20founded%20an%20agriculture%20startup%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20in%202016%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20supporting%20farmers%20around%20the%20globe.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20where%20his%20late%20grandfather%20worked%20as%20a%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarg%20has%20been%20building%20in%20India%20ever%20since%2C%20but%20he%20says%20its%20startup%20ecosystem%20cannot%20yet%20compete%20with%20the%20Valley's%20decades%20of%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20ecosystem%20was%20more%20mature%20back%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20It's%20still%20one%20of%20the%20best%20places%20for%20entrepreneurs.%20India%20isn't%20there%20yet%2C%20although%20it's%20growing%20pretty%20drastically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20ef