ecifically%20trying%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20more%20detail%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e9cea79-ff4c-41d7-a500-5569ad7572e6%5C%22%3EThe%20study%2C%20explained%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20research%20team%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%20San%20Diego%20School%20of%20Medicine%20and%20The%20Salk%20Institute%20wanted%20to%20test%20whether%20fasting%20could%20help%20people%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fmetabolic-syndrome-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emetabolic%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20risk%20factors%20for%20chronic%20illnesses.%20The%20condition%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-warning-signs-you-might-have-high-blood-sugar-doctors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20high%20levels%20of%20body%20fat%2C%20and%20increases%20the%20odds%20that%20someone%20will%20develop%20heart%20disease%20and%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20three%20months%2C%20the%20researchers%20followed%20108%20adults%20with%20metabolic%20syndrome%2C%20in%20theirs%2050s%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20the%20participants%20were%20randomly%20assigned%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3Eto%20follow%20their%20typical%20eating%20pattern%2C%20with%20some%20general%20nutrition%20advice%20about%20healthy%20eating%2C%20such%20as%20seeking%20inspiration%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterrean-diet-healthiest-best-overall-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20half%20were%20given%20the%20same%20advice%2C%20but%20were%20also%20instructed%20to%20limit%20their%20eating%20to%20eight%20to%2010%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20and%20tracked%20their%20eating%20on%20a%20smartphone%20app%20called%20myCircadianClock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20study%2C%20both%20groups%20lost%20a%20s