sible%2C'%20the%20letter%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20may%20ask%2C%20why%20make%20such%20a%20decision%20at%20this%20stage%3F%20I%20made%20this%20decision%20on%20the%20very%20day%20the%20accusations%20arose.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20accusations%20regarding%20the%20MUDA%20plot%20allocation%20were%20politically%20motivated%2C%20some%20well-wishers%20advised%20that%20we%20should%20fight%20against%20this%20injustice%20and%20not%20fall%20prey%20to%20their%20schemes.%20That's%20why%20I%20initially%20stepped%20back%20from%20returning%20the%20plots%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20husband%2C%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20has%20upheld%20a%20strict%20code%20of%20ethics%20throughout%20his%2040-year%20political%20career%2C%20remaining%20entirely%20free%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20blemish...%20To%20me%2C%20no%20house%2C%20plot%2C%20or%20wealth%20is%20more%20important%20than%20my%20husband's%20honor%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20peace%20of%20mind.%20After%20all%20these%20years%20in%20power%2C%20I%20have%20never%20sought%20any%20personal%20gain%20for%20myself%20or%20my%20family...%20I%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20my%20husband's%20opinion%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20concern%20myself%20with%20what%20my%20son%20or%20other%20family%20members%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20humbly%20appeal%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20members%20of%20the%20media.%20Please%20do%20not%20drag%20the%20women%20of%20political%20families%20into%20controversy%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20settling%20political%20scores.%20Do%20not%20harm%20their%20dignity%20and%20honor%20by%20involving%20them%20in%20political%20disputes%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20agency's%20case%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20filed%20by%20the%20Lokayukta%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20a%20special%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20brother-in-law%20Mallikarjuna%20Swamy%2C%20Devaraju%20and%20others%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20Lokayukta%20police%20on%20September%2027.%20Devaraju%20is%20the%20man%20from%20whom%20Mallikarjuna%20Swamy%20had%20purchased%20land%20and%20gifted%20it%20to%20Ms%20Parvathi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MUDA%20case%20involves%20allegations%20of%20illegalities%20in%20the%20allotment%20of%20Mysuru's%2014%20premium%20sites%20to%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20by%20the%20authority.%20It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20the%20value%20of%20the%20compensatory%20sites%20allotted%20to%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20--%20located%20in%20an%20upmarket%20area%20in%20Mysuru%20--%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20land%20acquired%20from%20her%20by%20MUDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20activists%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20allotment%20has%20led%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2045%20crore%20to%20the%20state.%20The%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20land%2C%20shown%20to%20be%20gifted%20to%20Ms%20Parvathi%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20was%20illegally%20acquired%20by%20her%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20Swamy%20had%20acquired%20the%20land%20in%202004%20using%20forged%20documents%20in%20connivance%20with%20government%20officials.%20The%20papers%20indicate%20that%20the%20land%20was%20purchased%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20are%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727718360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Facnhg56_siddaramaiah-pti_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-case-against-siddaramaiah-his-wife-offers-to-surrender-plots-to-mysuru-urban-develop