0after%20an%20ill-fated%20AN-12%20aircraft%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20crashed%20over%20the%20Rohtang%20Pass%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20bodies%20of%20four%20more%20victims%20were%20recovered%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20success%20in%20one%20of%20India's%20longest-running%20search%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20officials%20said%20the%20bodies%20were%20found%20by%20a%20joint%20team%20comprising%20personnel%20from%20the%20Dogra%20Scouts%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Tiranga%20Mountain%20Rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20twin-engine%20turboprop%20transport%20aircraft%2C%20carrying%20102%20people%2C%20had%20gone%20missing%20on%20February%207%2C%201968%20while%20flying%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20extraordinary%20development%2C%20the%20ongoing%20search%20and%20rescue%20mission%20to%20recover%20the%20remains%20of%20personnel%20from%20the%20AN-12%20aircraft%2C%20which%20crashed%20on%20Rohtang%20Pass%20in%201968%2C%20has%20achieved%20significant%20breakthroughs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20wreckage%20and%20remains%20of%20the%20victims%20remained%20lost%20in%20the%20icy%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%202003%20when%20mountaineers%20from%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Institute%20of%20Mountaineering%20discovered%20the%20wreckage%2C%20sparking%20multiple%20expeditions%20over%20the%20years%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20especially%20the%20Dogra%20Scouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dogra%20Scouts%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20search%20missions%20in%202005%2C%202006%2C%202013%2C%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20five%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20recovered%20by%202019%20in%20view%20of%20the%20treacherous%20conditions%20and%20unforgiving%20terrain%20of%20the%20crash%20site%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandra%20Bhaga%20Mountain%20Expedition%20has%20now%20recovered%20fo