an%20order%20of%20deputation%20of%20an%20army%20officer%20to%20civil%20police%20was%20issued%20without%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20commission%20when%20the%20MCC%20is%20still%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20government%20had%20on%20Monday%20issued%20the%20order%20of%20appointment%20of%20Colonel%20Vikrant%20Prasher%20as%20SSP%20(Training)%20and%20Special%20(Operation)%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20order%20taking%20exception%20to%20this%20move%20said%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20today%20in%20its%20letter%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Commission%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20force%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20as%20such%20there%20is%20a%20ban%20on%20transfer%20of%20officers%20connected%20to%20election%20is%20in%20force.%20Without%20going%2C%20at%20this%20stage%20into%20the%20rationale%2C%20process%20and%20urgency%20of%20posting%20an%20Army%20officer%20as%20SSP%20on%20the%20civil%20side%20during%20the%20period%20of%20operation%20of%20MCC%2C%20the%20Commission%20hereby%20directs%20that%20the%20order%20shall%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20If%20the%20order%20has%20been%20issued%20executed%2C%20the%20position%20before%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20order%20shall%20be%20restored%20with%20immediate%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20added%20that%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20shall%20send%20the%20compliance%20report%20by%2011%20am%20on%20October%201%20with%20an%20explanation%20as%20to%20why%20such%20an%20order%20was%20issued%20without%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikrant%20Prasher%20of%20the%20Parachute%20Regiment%20has%20already%20been%20cleared%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20for%20a%20two-year%20deputation%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Shaurya%20Chakra%20awardee%2C%20Prasher%20belongs%20to%20Udhampur%20district%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20he%20has%20distinguished%2