%20a%20union%20of%20revenue%20officers%2C%20has%20staged%20a%20dharna%20at%20Nawabganj%20Police%20Station%20demanding%20the%20registration%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Ukhra%20village%2C%20where%20a%20team%20of%20district%20administration%20on%20Saturday%20razed%20several%20structures%20built%20on%20government%20land%20using%20bulldozers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20when%20some%20BJP%20leaders%20reached%20the%20village%20and%20were%20talking%20to%20the%20people%20with%20Circle%20officer%20Arun%20Kumar%2C%20SHO%20Balraj%20Bhati%2C%20some%20of%20the%20villagers%20became%20violent%20and%20attacked%20Lekhpals%20(revenue%20officers)%20Rudra%20Pratap%20Singh%20and%20Saurabh%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20somehow%20dispersed%20the%20mob%20and%20controlled%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20President%20of%20Lekhpal%20Sangh%2C%20Ajit%20Dwivedi%20said%20his%20colleagues%20were%20brutally%20beaten%20up%20and%20their%20records%20were%20snatched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20injured.%20The%20Lekhpal%20Sangh%20will%20protest%20at%20the%20police%20station%20until%20a%20case%20is%20registered%20and%20the%20accused%20are%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20four%20bulldozers%20were%20used%20to%20demolish%20the%20structures%20on%20a%20barren%20land%20encroached%20upon%20for%20years%20in%20the%20village%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadar%20Tehsildar%20Shraddha%20Pandey%20had%20said%20about%20one-and-a-half%20hectares%20of%20land%20has%20been%20acquired%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20village%20society%20for%20the%20green%20energy%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20land%20was%20illegally%20occupied%20by%20some%20people.%20It%20is%20being%20freed%20from%20encroachments.%20All%20illegal%20constructions%20will%20be%20razed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%2017-second%20video%20on%20X%20in%20which%20bulldozers%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20action%2C%20SP%20chief%20Yadav%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20ugly%20face%20of%20BJP%20politics%20full%20of%20revenge.%20BJP%20gets%20happiness%20in%20demolishing%20settled%20houses.%20Those%20who%20have%20not%20settled%20their%20own%20houses%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20revenge%20they%20take%20for%20by%20demolishing%20the%20houses%20of%20others.%20With%20every%20falling%20house%2C%20BJP%20also%20falls%20even%20lower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20Amritkaal's%20information%3A%20Today%2C%20in%20village%20Ukhra%20of%20Amritpur%20assembly%20constituency%20of%20Farrukhabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20(constituency)%2C%20by%20running%20bulldozers%20on%20the%20houses%20of%2025%20poor%20families%20settled%20for%20years%2C%20who%20knows%20how%20many%20old%20people%2C%20sick%20people%20were%20rendered%20homeless%20in%20the%20rains.%20This%20is%20the%20height%20of%20political%20cruelty.%26quot%3B%20While%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20against%20bulldozer%20actions%20in%20various%20states%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20September%2017%20passed%20an%20interim%20order%20that%20no%20demolition%20of%20properties%20should%20take%20place%20in%20the%20country%20without%20its%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20the%20order%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20encroachments%20on%20public%20roads%2C%20footpaths%2C%20railway%20lines%2C%20or%20other%20public%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727709900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fl3donp28_ayodhya-bulldozer-_625x300_03_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n