%2C%20but%20Morkel%20said%20his%20wards%20kept%20themselves%20ready%20for%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20nice%20losing%20time%20and%20days.%20I%20knew%20the%20boys%20sitting%20around%20the%20hotel%2C%20that%20was%20sort%20of%20very%20frustrating.%20But%20the%20way%20the%20guys%20went%20off%20the%20field%2C%20still%20doing%20their%20gym%20work%2C%20looking%20after%20their%20bodies%2C%20was%20impressive%20to%20see%20for%20me%20coming%20into%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%2C%20once%20we%20get%20the%20opportunity%2C%20we're%20always%20going%20to%20look%20at%20the%20positive%20way%20and%20how%20we%20can%20impact%20that.%20Throughout%20the%20day%2C%20we%20showed%20the%20intent%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20was%20not%20surprised%20at%20all%20to%20see%20Indian%20batters%20going%20all%20guns%20blazing%20in%20their%20first%20innings%2C%20considering%20the%20lost%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20boys%20went%20to%20the%20ball%20up-front%2C%20it%20was%20incredible%20to%20see.%20We%20created%20the%20pressure%20(with%20the%20ball)%20and%20brought%20wickets%2C%20and%20then%20to%20show%20the%20intent%20with%20the%20bat%20was%20awesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20a%20part%20of%20our%20game%20plan%20to%20see%2C%20how%20can%20we%20push%20this%20going%20forward%3F%20And%20how%20can%20we%20get%20the%20winning%20result%3F%26quot%3B%20When%20their%20turn%20came%20to%20bowl%2C%20India%20quickly%20reduced%20Bangladesh%20to%2026%20for%20two%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20and%20for%20Morkel%20Test%20cricket%20is%20all%20about%20creating%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20do%20that%20for%20a%20long%20period%2C%20you'll%20get%20results.%20I%20think%20there's%20so%20much%20experience%2C%20these%20guys%20that%20can%20sum%20up%20the%20conditions%20very%20well%2C%20so%20they%20know%20what's%20important%20in%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20executing%20it.%20You%20can%20have%20the%20best%20laid%20plans%2C%20but%20if%20you%20can't%20execute%20it%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20fall%20short.%20But%20this%20group%20so%20far%20has%20been%20on%20the%20money%2C%20great%20to%20see%20how%20we%20adapt%20to%20conditions.%26quot%3B%20Morkel%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20the%20Indian%20batters'%20approach%2C%20especially%20Rishabh%20Pant%20changing%20tactics%20and%20playing%20to%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20said%20that%20the%20flexible%20approach%20gives%20the%20team%20a%20lot%20of%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20guys%20that%20can%20play%20different%20styles.%20If%20needed%2C%20they%20can%20take%20the%20game%20on.%20If%20needed%2C%20they%20can%20bat%20time.%20That's%20one%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20our%20batting%20line-up%20is%20that%20we've%20got%20guys%20that%20can%20really%20sort%20of%20play%20the%20moment%20and%20put%20bowlers%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20one%20thing%20you%20want%20to%20do%20as%20a%20batter%2C%20is%20to%20put%20the%20bowlers%20under%20pressure.%20We've%20got%20the%20guys%20that%20know%20how%20to%20score%20big%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20lauded%20the%20Indian%20team's%20professionalism%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20privilege%20for%20him%20to%20be%20in%20this%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20so%20far%2C%20so%20enjoyable%20to%20see%20how%20professional%20they%20are%20and%20how%20they%20go%20about%20their%20daily%20life%20to%20put%20on%20a%20performance.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20recovery%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20right%20up%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20gym%20work%2C%20fitness%20work%2C%20they%20honestly%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned.%20I'm%20not%20surprised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added