my%20baby%20for%20six%20months.%20Their%2024%C3%977%20WhatsApp%20community%20is%20amazing.%20All%20our%20queries%20are%20answered%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20My%20child%20is%20more%20than%20a%20year%20old%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20still%20breastfeeding%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowerment%20through%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20on%20traditional%20marketing%20strategies%2C%20Gayathri%20focused%20on%20connecting%20with%20her%20audience%20through%20educational%20content%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%20By%20posting%20informative%20videos%20on%20topics%20ranging%20from%20breastfeeding%20techniques%20to%20personal%20narratives%20of%20mothers%2C%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20inspire%20and%20educate%20its%20audience.%20Gayathri%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20creating%20a%20genuine%20impact%20rather%20than%20merely%20chasing%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20that%20for%20their%20three%20and%20six-month%20plans%2C%20the%20startup%20charges%20between%20Rs%204%2C500%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20It%20also%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20supportive%20ecosystem%20by%20offering%20affordable%20programmes%20and%20connecting%20mothers%20to%20free%20valuable%20resources%2C%20prioritising%20the%20well-being%20of%20both%20mothers%20and%20their%20babies%20over%20monetary%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%20is%20currently%20at%20a%20break-even%20stage%2C%20it%20is%20exploring%20partnerships%20with%20clinics%20and%20hospitals%20to%20reach%20more%20mothers%20and%20make%20its%20services%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Women%20Startup%20Programme%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20been%20incubated%20at%20NSRCEL%20(Nadathur%20S%20Raghavan%20Centre%20for%20Entrepreneurial%20Learning)%2C%20IIM%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGayathri%20feels%20deeply%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20impact%20her%20company%20is%20making.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20