ime%2C%20I%20found%20it%20was%20very%20effective%20in%20checking%20weed%20growth.%20This%20controlled%20the%20weed%20growth%20for%20six%20to%20eight%20months.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20improved%20soil%20quality%20by%20making%20it%20more%20porous%20and%20allowing%20roots%20to%20grow%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saravanan%20says%20the%20crop%20residues%20also%20decompose%20and%20release%20nutrients%2C%20resulting%20in%20fewer%20pest%20attacks%20and%20diseases.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20improves%20the%20carbon%2Fnitrogen%20ratio%20in%20soil.%20So%20it%20was%20an%20overall%20improvement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDriving%20profits%2C%20harvesting%20happiness%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20scientist-turned-farmer%20has%20redefined%20the%20concept%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303221%2Fkerala-engineer-turned-farmer-starts-moringa-mango-organic-farm-in-melbourne-australia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoringa%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20harmonious%20blend%20of%20science%20and%20nature.%20By%20shade-drying%20moringa%20leaves%2C%20he%20transforms%20them%20into%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%2C%20such%20as%20powder%2C%20capsules%2C%20and%20soups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20he%20earns%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20investing%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20acre%2C%20farmers%20can%20fetch%20up%20to%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20annually%20just%20by%20selling%20their%20leaves.%20If%20they%20venture%20into%20value%20addition%2C%20they%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20to%20double%20the%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20leveraging%20his%20expertise%20in%20soil%20science%20and%20agriculture%2C%20Dr%20Sarvanan%20has%20not%20only%20transformed%20the%20fortunes%20of%20his%20family%20farm%20but%2