%20was%20prime.%20She%20decided%20to%20keep%20financial%20independence%20for%20women%20at%20the%20fore.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ensured%20this%20while%20providing%20them%20%5Bthe%20women%5D%20skill%20training%20to%20hone%20their%20entrepreneurial%20ability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20module%20rests%20on%20the%20backbone%20that%20credit%20alone%20will%20not%20suffice.%20Skill%20training%20and%20coaching%20are%20vital%20to%20sustaining%20a%20business.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20so%2C%20we%20train%20these%20women%20in%20group%20dynamics%2C%20benefits%20of%20savings%2C%20interest%20computation%2C%20and%20financial%20and%20functional%20literacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20watching%20the%20women%20grow%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20relish%20their%20newfound%20independence%20thrills%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20World%20Bank%20report%20underscores%20how%2079%20percent%20of%20rural%20households%20do%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325587%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-runs-lending-platform-for-rural-indian-women-loans-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20a%20formal%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%2097%20percent%20of%20households%20without%20a%20formal%20loan%20report%20not%20having%20applied%20for%20a%20loan%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20The%20reasons%20they%20cite%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20need%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccomplicated%20procedures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20her%20work%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20has%20ensured%20over%20a%20million%20poor%20people%20have%20secured%20employment%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2